{"id":380917441,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"2 years, 4 months","timestamp":1597433725,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"12 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/380917441/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"6.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n  int minDistance(const string &s1, const string &s2)\n{\n   int N1 = s1.size();\n   int N2 = s2.size();\n   int i, j;\n   vector<int> T(N2+1);\n\n   for ( i = 0; i <= N2; i++ )\n      T[i] = i;\n\n   for ( i = 0; i < N1; i++ ) \n   {\n      T[0] = i+1;\n      int corner = i;\n      for ( j = 0; j < N2; j++ ) \n      {\n         int upper = T[j+1];\n         if ( s1[i] == s2[j] )\n            T[j+1] = corner;\n         else\n            T[j+1] = min(T[j], min(upper, corner)) + 1;\n         corner = upper;\n      }\n   }\n   return T[N2];\n}\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance","has_notes":false,"notes":"","topic_tags":[]}
